  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dd3.\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The incident at the Prime Minister's house is handed over to the CID",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Criminal Investigation Department has handed over the investigation into the incident of breaking into and setting fire to the private residence of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Inspector General of Police Mr. CD Wickramaratne assigned these investigations to the investigation department today (10).",
        "Police sources say that a team of the Criminal Investigation Department has already visited the Prime Minister's private residence and started investigations."
      ],
